<h4 id="_4-2-1-目标" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-2-1-目标" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.2.1 目标</h4>
<p>Validation用于校验是特别方便的，但是官方提供的注解可能不满足自己的需要，因此自定义注解用于数据校验</p>
<h4 id="_4-2-1-定义注解" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-2-1-定义注解" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.2.1 定义注解</h4>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token annotation punctuation">@Target</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">ElementType</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token constant">FIELD</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
